   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>[Has brought] Potammon(?), for the village of Karanis, for the second indiction, through Isidoros, two-hundred and forty litrai of chaff, = 240 litrai only. I, Theodotos, have signed.</ab>
         </div>
